Package: com.spotc.spothaptics
Name: SpotHaptics
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: Custom CoreHaptics playback for SpotC++.
 Bridges Spotify's playback engine to Apple's CoreHaptics framework,
 playing bundled .ahap haptic patterns in sync with songs.
